{"tid":1579264,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"隻貓絕食","createTime":"2019-09-18T13:28:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T00:09:36.000Z","uid":255802,"like":43,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"feb4a54b88a5300ff808733b6b2183d8c4e2793a","tid":1579264,"uid":255802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T13:28:56.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n屋企就養左2隻夜瘋魔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/18/212107_91ecb8774a270a3ea87307c7879b8932.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F18%2F212107_91ecb8774a270a3ea87307c7879b8932.jpg&h=ae5a794c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5個月大 都幾痴小妹架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當正我係佢地老母咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但事關小妹尋日暈低入左廠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原本以為2-3日就走得<br />\n仆佢個街 點知撚柒醫生話要住一個星期check好先走得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過好彩同老母住 <br />\n所以2隻野由佢照顧住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n。<br />\n問題黎啦 <br />\n老母就話兩隻貓成日幾乎唔飲唔食唔屙<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(應該發現隡屎條友唔見左好耐)<br />\n又好似淚汪汪想喊咁<br />\n點樣先可以餵到佢地食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n太耐唔食會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0U0qRbH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0U0qRbH.png&h=89d9e128&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上面係gorgor<br />\n下面依隻係muimui"},{"pid":"aa7669384bd2f4e3ba2c3b0bb4e62dcf0b624ad3","tid":1579264,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T13:29:06.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球響應「929全球集會抗赤納粹」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全世界一齊對準極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577380</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWqVmOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWqVmOV.jpg&h=075c7745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1tov9s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1tov9s.png&h=0af09f95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"000345d373db381b9af5bbe5fa74a94dee16c53e","tid":1579264,"uid":255802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T13:29:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"546f3bd3214260608fc98e212058793a8e0a1230","tid":1579264,"uid":255802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T13:30:00.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"ab0fc36b563952b2855ee57f21dbc78425908ac9","tid":1579264,"uid":255802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T13:30:10.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"4daf9e07026b1098d1d73b578a73610aa9192da7","tid":1579264,"uid":248394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T13:31:10.000Z","msg":"快啲好返 幫推"},{"pid":"603762a56f44b134bed6f3d9601cb8cd65d1ad8b","tid":1579264,"uid":281701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T13:31:19.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\nBtw開罐鹿肉佢啖下睇下食唔食"},{"pid":"05fe7cb9d5bf028118a5144354218ed92ea22597","tid":1579264,"uid":37389,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T13:31:23.000Z","msg":"貓唔肯食嘢低急症嚟架。。。幾年前我隻貓試過，打去九條命，以前無睇過，都肯即刻被我打尖"},{"pid":"02de350ba545b3aec519e34119b6eb593617c8df","tid":1579264,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T13:32:13.000Z","msg":"可唔可以比我玩"},{"pid":"028afe5379763f2e360178af7671ee944ab14437","tid":1579264,"uid":255802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"603762a56f44b134bed6f3d9601cb8cd65d1ad8b","tid":1579264,"uid":281701,"li